social_posts.post_text: The 2022-2023 ski season has begun! #jfbb

I feel so lucky. So lucky to have worked with the greatest. So lucky to have watched him work. So lucky to have learned from the very best. And now, I am so excited to take all he taught our team about great broadcast journalism, the city of Philadelphia, the covenant we keep with our viewers and carry on the legacy built by this great man. Thank you, Jim.
We are ready.
